Marcelle Géniat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcelle_G%C3%A9niat 0 Marcelle Géniat (1881-1959) was a French film actress.She was born Eugénie Pauline Martin in St. Petersburg, Russia, to French parents.
